  <HighlightBar text="17 inspectors general fired unlawfully. Zero documents for 70+ subpoenas. DOGE operating without Senate confirmation. GAO found spending freezes illegal. The separation of powers exists for a reason — and it is being dismantled." />

  <CTASection
    title="Three Branches.<br>One Trying to Absorb the Others."
    description="The Founders designed a system of checks and balances because they understood the danger of concentrated power. Inspectors general, congressional oversight, the power of the purse — each check is being eroded."
